snippet: Russian security forces killed six rebels suspected of involvement in a suicide bombing on Thursday that left four police officers dead in the province of Dagestan, officials said.
abstract: Russian security forces track and kill six rebels suspected of involvement in suicide bombing that left four police officers dead in southern province of Dagestan.
lead_paragraph: Russian security forces killed six rebels suspected of involvement in a suicide bombing on Thursday that left four police officers dead in the province of Dagestan, officials said.
